<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>A</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lawmhnak le hawikomhnak tha ka hmuh cang, A zungzal, A tang chungah ka
 um, Lunglawmhnak le daihnak ah ka um cang, A zungzal a tang chungah ka um.

[C1]
   Amah hngatchan, Tihphannak in ka luat dih cang, Amah hngat chan, A
   zungzal a tang chungah ka um.

[V2]
 Lam ka kal lioah phannak a um lo, A zungzal, A tang chungah ka um,
 Nifate in lam a ceu chin lengmang, A zungzal a tang chungah ka um.

[C2]
   Amah hngatchan, Tihphannak in ka luat dih cang, Amah hngat chan, A
   zungzal a tang chungah ka um.

[V3]
 Phannak le tihnak a um kho hnga maw, A zungzal, A tang chungah ka um,
 Bawipa naih tikah, Lawmhnak kha ka hmuh, A zungzal a tang chungah ka um.

[C3]
   Amah hngatchan, Tihphannak in ka luat dih cang, Amah hngat chan, A
   zungzal a tang chungah ka um.</lyrics>
<title>A TANG CHUNGAH KA UM! CH73</title>
<hymn_number>73</hymn_number>
</song>